---

---

<section class="py-24 bg-cream">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <span
                class="inline-block text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-sage mb-4"
                >The Difference</span
            >
            <h2
                class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-semibold text-forest mb-4 tracking-tight"
            >
                Why Skip the Supermarket?
            </h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                When you buy from the supermarket, you're paying for middlemen,
                warehouses, and mystery meat. Here's what you get when you buy
                direct from us.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
            <div
                class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border-2 border-gray-200 relative"
            >
                <div
                    class="absolute -top-4 left-8 bg-gray-400 text-white px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold"
                >
                    Supermarket Beef
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-6 mt-4">
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                        <div
                            class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"
                        >
                            <svg
                                class="w-4 h-4 fill-red-500"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                ><path
                                    d="M19 6.41L17.59 5 12 10.59 6.41 5 5 6.41 10.59 12 5 17.59 6.41 19 12 13.41 17.59 19 19 17.59 13.41 12z"
                                ></path></svg
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-1">
                                Unknown Origin
                            </h4>
                            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
                                Could be from anywhere in Australia—or overseas.
                                You'll never know which farm or how it was
                                raised.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                        <div
                            class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"
                        >
                            <svg
                                class="w-4 h-4 fill-red-500"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                ><path
                                    d="M19 6.41L17.59 5 12 10.59 6.41 5 5 6.41 10.59 12 5 17.59 6.41 19 12 13.41 17.59 19 19 17.59 13.41 12z"
                                ></path></svg
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-1">
                                Weeks Old
                            </h4>
                            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
                                Sits in warehouses, trucks, and display cases.
                                By the time you eat it, it's been packaged for
                                weeks.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                        <div
                            class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"
                        >
                            <svg
                                class="w-4 h-4 fill-red-500"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                ><path
                                    d="M19 6.41L17.59 5 12 10.59 6.41 5 5 6.41 10.59 12 5 17.59 6.41 19 12 13.41 17.59 19 19 17.59 13.41 12z"
                                ></path></svg
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-1">
                                Feedlot Finished
                            </h4>
                            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
                                Most supermarket beef spends its final months in
                                feedlots, grain-fed to fatten quickly.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                        <div
                            class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"
                        >
                            <svg
                                class="w-4 h-4 fill-red-500"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                ><path
                                    d="M19 6.41L17.59 5 12 10.59 6.41 5 5 6.41 10.59 12 5 17.59 6.41 19 12 13.41 17.59 19 19 17.59 13.41 12z"
                                ></path></svg
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-1">
                                Paying for Middlemen
                            </h4>
                            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
                                Processors, distributors, retailers—everyone
                                takes a cut before it reaches your trolley.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                        <div
                            class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"
                        >
                            <svg
                                class="w-4 h-4 fill-red-500"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                ><path
                                    d="M19 6.41L17.59 5 12 10.59 6.41 5 5 6.41 10.59 12 5 17.59 6.41 19 12 13.41 17.59 19 19 17.59 13.41 12z"
                                ></path></svg
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-1">
                                Zero Connection
                            </h4>
                            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
                                Just a barcode on plastic wrap. No story, no
                                farmer, no accountability.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div
                class="bg-linear-to-br from-forest to-forest-light rounded-2xl p-8 relative text-cream"
            >
                <div
                    class="absolute -top-4 left-8 bg-mint text-forest px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold"
                >
                    Ferguson Livestock
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-6 mt-4">
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                        <div
                            class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-mint/20 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"
                        >
                            <svg
                                class="w-4 h-4 fill-mint-light"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                ><path
                                    d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"
                                ></path></svg
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-semibold text-cream mb-1">
                                From Our Paddock
                            </h4>
                            <p class="text-sm text-cream/80">
                                You know exactly where it comes from—our family
                                farm in Snake Valley. Come visit anytime.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                        <div
                            class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-mint/20 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"
                        >
                            <svg
                                class="w-4 h-4 fill-mint-light"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                ><path
                                    d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"
                                ></path></svg
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-semibold text-cream mb-1">
                                Freshly Processed
                            </h4>
                            <p class="text-sm text-cream/80">
                                From processing to your freezer in days, not
                                weeks. Vacuum-sealed at peak freshness.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                        <div
                            class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-mint/20 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"
                        >
                            <svg
                                class="w-4 h-4 fill-mint-light"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                ><path
                                    d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"
                                ></path></svg
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-semibold text-cream mb-1">
                                100% Grass-Fed, Always
                            </h4>
                            <p class="text-sm text-cream/80">
                                Our Murray Greys live on pasture their entire
                                lives. No feedlots, no grain, no hormones—ever.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                        <div
                            class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-mint/20 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"
                        >
                            <svg
                                class="w-4 h-4 fill-mint-light"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                ><path
                                    d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"
                                ></path></svg
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-semibold text-cream mb-1">
                                Fair Price, More Value
                            </h4>
                            <p class="text-sm text-cream/80">
                                No middlemen means better beef at a better
                                price. Your money goes directly to the farmer.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                        <div
                            class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-mint/20 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"
                        >
                            <svg
                                class="w-4 h-4 fill-mint-light"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                ><path
                                    d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"
                                ></path></svg
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-semibold text-cream mb-1">
                                We Deliver It Ourselves
                            </h4>
                            <p class="text-sm text-cream/80">
                                We'll shake your hand when we drop it off. Have
                                questions? Ask us directly.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
